title: Vertex AI - List sync operations
abstract:
# Vertex AI - List sync operations
**    Preview     ** This feature is subject to the "Pre-GA Offerings Terms" in the General Service Terms section   of the [Service Specific Terms](/terms/service-terms#1) .     Pre-GA features are available "as is" and might have limited support.    For more information, see the [launch stage descriptions](/products#product-launch-stages) .
You can view the list of data sync operations executed for a specific feature view. This can be useful if you want to verify whether the data sync is being successfully synced from the BigQuery data source, or whether data sync is currently in progress for the feature view.
